ata |last=Ss |date=2 April 2020 |website=Mbl |language=En |access-date=3 April 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200403102907/https://www.covid.is/data |archive-date=3 April 2020 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{flagdeco|EST}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Estonia|Estonia]]\n|1,535\n|40\n|165\n|<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.err.ee/1064218/koroonaviirusesse-on-eestis-nakatunud-135-inimest |title=Koroonaviirusesse on Eestis nakatunud 135 inimest |publisher=ERR |language=Estonian |trans-title=135 people have already been diagnosed with coronavirus in Estonia |access-date=15 March 2020}}</ref><ref name=\"terviseamet\">{{cite web |url=https://www.terviseamet.ee/et/uuskoroonaviirus |title=Koroonaviiruse haigus COVID-19 &#124; Terviseamet |publisher=Terviseamet.ee |language=et |access-date=2020-03-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200330141010/https://www.terviseamet.ee/et/uuskoroonaviirus |archive-date=30 March 2020 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{flagdeco|Slovenia}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Slovenia|Slovenia]]\n|1,335\n|77\n|193\n|<ref>[https://www.gov.si/teme/koronavirus/ Koronavirus COVID-19] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200313201048/https://www.gov.si/teme/koronavirus/ |date=13 March 2020}} ''www.gov.si'', accessed 12 March 2020</ref>\n|-\n|{{flagdeco|LTU}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Lithuania|Lithuania]]\n|1,326\n|37\n|242\n|<ref>[https://koronastop.lrv.lt/ Svarbiausia informacija apie koronavirus\u0105 (COVID-19)] ''lrv.lt''accessed 14 April 2020</ref>\n|-\n|{{flagdeco|BIH}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Bosnia and Herzegovina|Bosnia and Herzegovina]]\n|1,309\n|49\n|381\n|\n|-\n|{{flagdeco|MKD}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in North Macedonia|North Macedonia]]\n|1,225\n|54\n|200\n|<ref>{{cite web |url=https://makfax.com.mk/makedonija/%d0%b2%d0%b8%d0%b4%d0%b5%d0%be-%d1%83%d1%88%d1%82%d0%b5-%d1%88%d0%b5%d1%81%d1%82-%d0%bb%d0%b8%d1%86%d0%b0-%d0%bf%d0%be%d0%b7%d0%b8%d1%82%d0%b8%d0%b2%d0%bd%d0%b8-%d0%bd%d0%b0-%d